{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f338247107","title":"关于修筑进藏公路的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"840c057390","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"f338247107"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"808abf1111","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中国人民解放军西北军区张宗逊（第一副司令员）、甘泗淇（副政治委员兼政治部主任）、商摸要（参谋长）1951年6月7日给军委并报西北局的电报上的批语。张宗逊等在电报中谈到进军西藏的军事部署、补给、修筑道路等问题，提出：（一）建议今年继续修通张披至西宁公路（360公里），以便于油料的补给。（二）立即准备1952年春开工修筑的黄河沿至玉树公路。（三）立即着手分段勘测玉树至囊谦及敦煌经柴达木、唐古拉山口、黑河至拉萨线。"},{"id":"956b7a4715","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"楚，指费荣臻，当时任中国人民解放军代总参谋长。"},{"id":"c9333fa67c","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ccd05cfcee","type":"title","text":"关于修筑进藏公路的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107"},{"id":"808abf1111","type":"subtitle","text":"慧：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107"},{"id":"956b7a4715","type":"paragraph","text":"是否有钱修这些路，请与陈云时同志商的，可缓者应一律从缓。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107"},{"id":"c9333fa67c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107"},{"id":"08d7a523c3","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107"}],"page":{"id":"d25336ff85","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f338247107","start":36